Package org.jlab.icalibrate.model

Provides the iCalibrate object model classes.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ChartDataset
    Models a JFreeChart dataset capable of providing a fit.
    CreateNewDatasetParameters
    Models the process input parameters required to create a new hall calibration dataset.
    DoseRateMeasurement
    Models a dose rate measurement or average dose rate measurement value at a specified current.
    DoseRateTripSetpoint
    Models the dose rate setpoint for a given ion chamber.
    HallCalibrationDataset
    Models a hall calibration dataset with all metadata.
    IonChamber
    Models and ion chamber and all of the metadata associated with it.
    IonChamberDataset
    Models the measured dose rate data for a given ion chamber.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Hall
    Models the finite set of halls at JLab which are eligible for ion chamber calibration.
    Laser
    Models the finite set of injector lasers at JLab.
